<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.2.2">
<l>vallicēr nuṇṇiṭai yāycciyar tammoṭuṅ</l>
<l>kollaimai ceytu kuravai piṇaintavar</l>
<l>nallaṭi mēlaṇi nāṟu tuḻāyeṉṟē</l>
<l>collumāl cūḻviṉai yāṭṭiyēṉ pāvaiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>“The fragrant Tulsi [that is the] decoration on the good feet</l>
<l>of him who joined in the Kuravai [dance], transgressing propriety,</l>
<l>with all the cowherdesses with waists thin as creepers”,</l>
<l>thus speaks the daughter of me [who is] a woman of engulfing [past] deeds.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
